tip.text: Red grouper fish is really fresh and price is reasonable for this kind of quality. If you compare the price with other locations, you will never get such a good deal. Value for money! Do try it out!
we have been here for a few time already, every time I came I will order a set of Wagyu beef with fish milk soup.I recommend this place for team buildings as it suits everyone 's taste!
Eat the fish and milk soup again, with wagyu beef!!! Hot weather I still like to eat hot pot!
